This project includes code and implementation logic derived from ezDyson.

Collaboration and affiliation:
- Developed in collaboration with the Mabbs Group, Department of Chemistry, Washington University in St. Louis.

Upstream project:
- ezDyson (USC iOpenShell)
- https://iopenshell.usc.edu/downloads/ezdyson/

