Please cite ezDyson as requested by upstream:
- S. Gozem and A. I. Krylov, "The ezSpectra suite: An easy-to-use toolkit for spectroscopy modeling", WIREs Comput. Mol. Sci., e1546 (2021).
- S. Gozem, A. O. Gunina, T. Ichino, D. L. Osborn, J. F. Stanton, and A. I. Krylov, J. Phys. Chem. Lett. 6, 4532-4540 (2015).

Project citation guidance:
- Prior to manuscript publication, cite the repository and reference the manuscript as "in preparation".
- After publication, add the full paper citation and DOI to this NOTICE and to README.

Original contributions in this project include workflow integration, continuum model extensions, averaging options, automation, and visualization.
